Summary: Like a speeding jet with yellowish lights.
divs: Sighting DetailsI stepped outside to smoke and checked out the sky as usual and noticed a fast moving light highup, I continued to watch it, so mystified I had to go to my backyard to continue but it disappeared behind a large dark cloud judy as soon as I arrived. it moved so fast it was unthinkable the speed it could be going in a straight line going north, north west. I wanted to try and get it on cellphone i was holding but I took my eyes off for 1 sec to figure it out and nearly lost sight of it so decided agaisnt the good idea.
